INSERT INTO tmdb_image_variants (
            image_variant, tmdb_path, media_id, media_type,
            width, height, iso_lang, vote_avg, vote_cnt, is_primary
        )
        VALUES (
            'profile'::image_variant, $1, $2, 'person'::media_type,
            0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, true
        )
        ON CONFLICT (tmdb_path) DO UPDATE SET
            media_id = EXCLUDED.media_id,
            media_type = EXCLUDED.media_type,
            image_variant = EXCLUDED.image_variant,
            is_primary = EXCLUDED.is_primary
        RETURNING id
